  "texts": [
    "Whereas this construction builds the worlds of the Kripke model out of ultrafilters in ⟨P, ⊆⟩, Harrison-Trainor's construction builds the worlds of the Kripke model out of ultrafilters in ⟨S, ⊑⟩.",
    "For a historical overview, see Goldblatt 2006a; for surveys of the theory, seeBlackburn and van Benthem 2007, Goldblatt 2006a, and Goranko and Otto 2007; and for textbooks, see, e.g.,Blackburn et al.",
